data.title: Herschweiler
meta_keywords: Meyers Gazetteer of the German Empire
data.meta_description: The historical entry for Herschweiler-Petersheim, Kusel, Pfalz, Bayern, including parish and jurisdiction information, in the Meyers Gazetteer of the German Empire also known as Meyers Orts- und Verkehrs-Lexikon des Deutschen Reichs.
data.text:
Type Gem. - Herschweiler-Petersheim is a Gemeinde (Community).

Lvl I Bay. - Level I shows which Kingdom or State the place is located in. Herschweiler-Petersheim is located in Bayern.

RB Pfalz - The Regierungsbezirk for Herschweiler-Petersheim is Pfalz. The Regierungsbezirk is a government district that is in hierarchy between the State and Kreis level.

BA Kusel - The Bezirksamt for Herschweiler-Petersheim is Kusel. The Bezirksamt is the District Office.

AG Kusel - The Amtsgericht for Herschweiler-Petersheim is in Kusel. The Amtsgericht is where the Lower District Court is located.

BKdo Kaiserslautern - The Bezirkskommando for Herschweiler-Petersheim is in Kaiserslautern. The Bezirkskommando is the District Military Command. You can look in the BKdo to find military records.

StdA Herschweiler-Petersheim [self] - The Standesamt for Herschweiler-Petersheim is in itself. The Standesamt is where the Civil Registration Office is located.
